**Chief Singh:** ...in the war, goof. I'm a Scarbs boy,[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]Scarborough, Ontario.[[/span]] but I've seen some shit. Why'd you think they gave me //this// job? 

